embers of great seniority and distinction in the Congress, and some very new members, who will no longer be serving with us.','Nancy Pelosi','sad'),(4323,'All he cares about is going out there with his Jack Daniels bottle. Nothing has changed. That\'s kind of sad. If David was doing better than he used to be, then that would be different. But it was a joke and he made it that way.','Sammy Hagar','sad'),(4324,'People say, oh it\'s a shame, you\'re not nostalgic about the \'60s. Well actually, it\'s quite good, when you think of it. Wouldn\'t it be sad if I was sitting here wishing it back?','Robert Wyatt','sad'),(4325,'Divorce was very sad, obviously, but now I\'ve gotten over it.','Natalie Imbruglia','sad'),(4326,'I like singer-songwriters, and I find sad songs comforting rather than depressing. It makes you realise you\'re not alone in the world.','Natalie Imbruglia','sad'),(4327,'I have had stalkers over the years. The police deal with it but it is very scary. One man kept turning up where we filmed \'Countdown in Leeds,\' which was scary. It was sad as he\'d been sectioned and thought I was talking to him through the TV.','Carol Vorderman','sad'),(4328,'\'The Taxi Ride,\' from my second album, is one people want to hear a lot. I\'m consciously trying to walk on the sunny side of the street, to really lift myself into a place of greater positivity, and that\'s a sad song.','Jane Siberry','sad'),(4329,'I find it amusing on one level, poignant on another, when people try to get recognition from an outside source. It\'s sad.','Grace Slick','sad'),(4330,'Ideally, I would love to mix singing and acting, but you can only be a pop star for so many years. I mean, at 30 it\'s a little bit sad, right?','Rachel Stevens','sad'),(4331,'I think a lot of people think that my parents\' deaths is why I write such sad songs, but that\'s not true. Those songs may just be the woman I am.','Shelby Lynne','sad'),(4332,'I\'m sad to see the passing of the great drug warriors. I certainly