k they don\'t have anything going on except being pretty.','Keri Russell','sad'),(7166,'It\'s sad to know I\'m done. But looking back, I\'ve got a lot of great memories.','Bonnie Blair','sad'),(7167,'This Olympics is almost a little sad. It is my final Olympics. There are a lot of good memories.','Bonnie Blair','sad'),(7168,'The day Dick Cheney is going to run for president, I\'ll kill myself. All we need is another liar... I think he\'d like to run, but it would be a sad day for the country if he does.','Helen Thomas','sad'),(7169,'You want people to feel something when you tell a story, whether they feel happy or whether they feel sad.','Harry Dean Stanton','sad'),(7170,'Well, you can\'t be depressed and sad 24 hours a day.','Julia Sweeney','sad'),(7171,'It is sad that the Republican leadership is not as interested as they say they are in protecting the institution of marriage as they are in waging a campaign to divide and distract the American people from the real issues that need to be addressed.','Kendrick Meek','sad'),(7172,'It would be sad if we lost our instinct and our courage to love and protect.','Emeli Sande','sad'),(7173,'I often say the last role I played that really touched me and where I was able to access what I really am was Bonnie, which is kind of sad when you think how early in my career that was.','Faye Dunaway','sad'),(7174,'I had to choose, I\'d be so sad. They are flip sides of the same coin. I love both comedy and drama.','Dianne Wiest','sad'),(7175,'I recently turned down a film that I didn\'t want my kids to see. Priorities shift. Sometimes I\'m sad about that, but not enough to do anything about it.','Dianne Wiest','sad'),(7176,'I was always depressed growing up. There wasn\'t a reason for it, I just was. I was sad and morose. I cried a lot, I wrote a lot, and I read a lot; and that was how I dealt with it.','Amanda Hocking','sad'),(7177,'There is the glamour side of it, which allows you to meet great variety of people with whom you simp